data.title: Dragon Ball Super: Series 1 Episode 22 Change! An Unexpected Return! His Name Is Ginyu!!
data.meta_description: Tagoma proves to be a tough opponent and even Piccolo can't take him. Gotenks joins the battle but suddenly Tagoma is taken over by Ginyu. Gohan is able to face him but can he keep up when Frieza makes his move?
data.text:
Dragon Ball Super

ABC Big KidsActionAnime

The threat of Majin Buu has passed, and Goku and friends are all living in peace. Then there appears Beerus, the God of Destruction. The story finally moves beyond the universe, into a new phase!
